The paper discusses a storage model for optimizing update operations in Hive, which is a data warehouse tool used for big data processing. This topic falls under the database (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and social and information networks (cs.SI) categories.
